values.value: The core Nut command is at the start of the chain. Each Parameter filter acts as a numerical gateway for more specific results based off numeric input with the core command.To add a new nut redeem and tie it to a specific number, create a parameter filter and follow the prescribed parameter structure. Once done, connect the gateway parameter filter to the second output in the ordered execution node below. Have fun!

blocks.title: Fist of the North Star Nut
